title: Mondo New York (1988)
description:
Somewhere between Uptown and Downtown,Heaven an Hell, Lies...

Mondo New York is the bittersweet core of the Big Apple, a perversely compelling tribute to the antistars of the city, a circa 1980's Berlin cabaret. Mondo New York is a cult classic celebration of what makes the naked city a one of a kind metropolis.
